channel.title: Forum RSCD control panel
channel.description: i have searched the forums over and over again and couldn't find an answer to my problem. sory if there is already an post with the answer but i am gonna ask it anyways lol when i go into the admin panel on the forums (rscd v25 with forums) and i click rscd control panel it says that the server must be down and redirects me to the status page... can anyone help me get the forums to detect the server and get the control panel working please and thank you.
